  <h2 id="aftermarket-parts">Alfa Laval Aftermarket Parts</h2>

  <p>
    <strong>Alfa Laval aftermarket parts are perfectly compatible parts for Alfa Laval centrifuges. High-quality manufacturers produce generic parts for Alfa Laval separators. They save money and time while providing the reliability of genuine parts.</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    Call us for reconditioned bowl assemblies and bowl parts for popular Alfa Laval models. We can even rebuild certain bowl parts worn out by long-term use. Visit our <a href="/disc-centrifuge-parts-glossary/">centrifuge parts glossary</a> to get familiar with the unique terminology of disc centrifuges.
  </p>

  <h2 id="bearing-warning">Centrifuge Bearing Warning</h2>

  <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-gold bg-navy/5 p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
    <p class="font-semibold italic">Industrial centrifuges use special high-speed rated bearings specially made for centrifuges. Do NOT replace centrifuge bearings with aftermarket, "off-the-shelf," cheap bearings.</p>
  </blockquote>
  <p>
    These bearings are not suitable for the high operating speeds of industrial centrifuges. Generic bearings can lead to <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge-vibration/">centrifuge vibrations</a> and possibly catastrophic failures.
  </p>

